{"tid":2280493,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★低收入家庭學童：長大後希望成為傳媒大亨","createTime":"2020-11-10T13:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T15:06:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b601577a1a3d6832d2591eeed4e9575f6566af2e","tid":2280493,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T13:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201110/photo/bkn-20201110201240265-1110_00842_001_01p.jpg?20201110201244\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20201110%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20201110201240265-1110_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20201110201244&h=968ca518&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n滙豐夥拍聖雅各福群會，向低收入家庭提供電子設備及工作坊。滙豐香港區行政總裁施穎茵(Diana)更到訪位於九龍灣的學校，與受惠學童交流，了解其對於網上學習的需要。<br />\n<br />\n僅讀小一、小二的學生相當健談，還向Diana透露，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>長大後希望成為傳媒大亨</strong></span>和游泳選手。Diana叫他們先要努力讀書，善用科技吸收更多知識，才可以實現理想，更有學生向Diana送贈由一幅由該校小一學生合力創作的水彩畫。<br />\n今年4月，滙豐宣布捐出6,000萬港元抗疫，惠及超過60萬低收入家庭、長者及弱勢社群，現在再加碼至7,000萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201110/bkn-20201110201240265-1110_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20201110%2Fbkn-20201110201240265-1110_00842_001.html&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7Ip2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=f358ba4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201110/bkn-20201110201240265-1110_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f668053baf756b1d53bf176718379f6feb61cd22","tid":2280493,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T13:47:21.000Z","msg":"老綜大亨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces